import React from 'react'
import './index.css'

export default function index() {
    return ( <
        div className = "footer" >
        <
        div className = "song" >
        <
        img src = "http://p2.music.126.net/0-nJ8SPNSa6go8ffehQjzQ==/109951165549840947.jpg"
        alt = "album art" / >
        <
        div className = "info" >
        <
        p className = "title" > 12 월엔(sad night) < /p> <
        p className = "artist" > $ÜN / JB < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        div className = "controls" >
        <
        span className = "fa fa-step-backward" > < /span> <
        span className = "fa fa-play" > < /span> <
        span className = "fa fa-step-forward" > < /span> <
        span className = "fa fa-repeat sm-hide" > < /span> <
        span className = "fa fa-like sm-hide" > < /span> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    )
}
